    <h2>10. International Data Transfers</h2>

    <h3>10.1 The App</h3>
    <p>The App does not transfer your data internationally -- or at all -- because your data stays on your device. When you choose to use LLM provider APIs, data flows directly from your device to the provider's servers. The location of those servers depends on the provider you choose:</p>
